
 The subdirectory html contains the full HTML documentation 
 on Healpix (point your browser to [HEALPIX]/doc/html/main.htm).

 The subdirectory pdf contains the full PDF documentation 

 The subdirectory epub contains the EPUB documentation

 See the script $HEALPIX/healpix_doc to easily access these documentations

 All documentations are also available at 
 https://healpix.sourceforge.io

